{
  "video_id": "DWOvnPZ9e7Y",
  "title": "Overcoming Dyslexia - An Award Winning Short Documentary",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 3400.0,
      "end_time": 9940.0,
      "text": "*City and Typewriter Sounds*"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12800.0,
      "end_time": 18180.0,
      "text": "*Music Fades In*"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 23100.0,
      "end_time": 26560.0,
      "text": "I have dyslexia. Um, I&#39;ve had it my entire life."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26560.0,
      "end_time": 28340.0,
      "text": "I think I was diagnosed with it"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28340.0,
      "end_time": 30580.0,
      "text": "when I was... young."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 38840.0,
      "end_time": 41940.0,
      "text": "I was diagnosed with it when I was in third grade."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 41940.0,
      "end_time": 44599.0,
      "text": "It was very  serious. I- I felt very stupid and dumb"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 44600.0,
      "end_time": 47940.0,
      "text": "and wishing that I could just disappear."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 57480.0,
      "text": "Really what we need is just more"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 57480.0,
      "end_time": 60860.0,
      "text": "education on the subject of dyslexia."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 75800.0,
      "end_time": 78940.0,
      "text": "Dyslexia is, you know, a broad term"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 78940.0,
      "end_time": 83390.0,
      "text": "for more of a language-based disability in reading."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 83400.0,
      "end_time": 85540.0,
      "text": "Your eyes, basically, take"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 85540.0,
      "end_time": 88660.0,
      "text": "pictures in a manner that either sets"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 88660.0,
      "end_time": 91660.0,
      "text": "words or letters backwards, or you"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 91660.0,
      "end_time": 93780.0,
      "text": "misplace words when you read."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 93780.0,
      "end_time": 97180.0,
      "text": "Just, the way they think and act is a lot different."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 97180.0,
      "end_time": 99340.0,
      "text": "I can write, but it&#39;s slow."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 99340.0,
      "end_time": 101800.0,
      "text": "So co-workers can sit there and whip out"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 101800.0,
      "end_time": 103539.0,
      "text": "reports, and I&#39;m still working on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 103540.0,
      "end_time": 106500.0,
      "text": "So they assume that since you can&#39;t read a"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 106500.0,
      "end_time": 109840.0,
      "text": "paragraph correctly that you are... stupid"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 109840.0,
      "end_time": 112580.0,
      "text": "or you&#39;re incapable of thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 112580.0,
      "end_time": 114520.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just the way that their brain was"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 114520.0,
      "end_time": 117360.0,
      "text": "designed, and... there&#39;s nothing wrong with"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 117360.0,
      "end_time": 119280.0,
      "text": "that. You know, if you saw someone who"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 119280.0,
      "end_time": 121480.0,
      "text": "physically couldn&#39;t walk up the stairs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 121480.0,
      "end_time": 124660.0,
      "text": "society wouldn&#39;t say \"What&#39;s your problem,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 124660.0,
      "end_time": 127140.0,
      "text": "or \"You need to learn to do it on your own.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 127140.0,
      "end_time": 129220.0,
      "text": "When they do set up the programs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 129220.0,
      "end_time": 130960.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re set up by people a lot of times"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 130960.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134200.0,
      "text": "that don&#39;t have... dyslexia. Therefore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 134200.0,
      "end_time": 136560.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re set up wrong from the beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 136560.0,
      "end_time": 138900.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had everything from teachers"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 138900.0,
      "end_time": 140980.0,
      "text": "telling me that my second grader isn&#39;t"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 140980.0,
      "end_time": 143780.0,
      "text": "trying hard. To teachers saying, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 143780.0,
      "end_time": 146440.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not going to help your son unless he"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 146440.0,
      "end_time": 148000.0,
      "text": "comes and asks for help."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 148000.0,
      "end_time": 149560.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ll give you more time."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 149560.0,
      "end_time": 153420.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s one of the answers in school for dyslexic people."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 153420.0,
      "end_time": 156339.0,
      "text": "And it cracks me up, because it&#39;s just more time to"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 156340.0,
      "end_time": 158220.0,
      "text": "stare at the book. Well they read slower"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 158220.0,
      "end_time": 160780.0,
      "text": "so they ne- need more time. Well they"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 160780.0,
      "end_time": 161940.0,
      "text": "can&#39;t read at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 161940.0,
      "end_time": 165400.0,
      "text": "Uh, my full name is Aaron Austin. And the stuff that I do"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 165400.0,
      "end_time": 167480.0,
      "text": "with Mrs. Jen helps me read."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 167480.0,
      "end_time": 169840.0,
      "text": "When I started working, actually working with him one-on-one"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 169840.0,
      "end_time": 171519.0,
      "text": "he was in fifth grade, and he was still"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 171520.0,
      "end_time": 173100.0,
      "text": "reading at a kindergarten level."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 173100.0,
      "end_time": 176560.0,
      "text": "It was very... um... he needed that one-on-one attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176560.0,
      "end_time": 179220.0,
      "text": "Well, I think she sees a lot of herself in Aaron."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 179220.0,
      "end_time": 184300.0,
      "text": "That was me. And I took Aaron under my wing because..."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 184300.0,
      "end_time": 186600.0,
      "text": "...no child should be left that way. Ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 186600.0,
      "end_time": 189660.0,
      "text": "I like Mrs. Jen, because she is nice to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 189660.0,
      "end_time": 191400.0,
      "text": "and she understands me."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 191400.0,
      "end_time": 193200.0,
      "text": "Society makes you feel very isolated"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 193200.0,
      "end_time": 194679.0,
      "text": "when you have it, because you don&#39;t learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 194680.0,
      "end_time": 196140.0,
      "text": "the same way as other people."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 196140.0,
      "end_time": 198940.0,
      "text": "I know that Bill was... segregated from the rest of"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 198940.0,
      "end_time": 201480.0,
      "text": "the class and put into special ed classes."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201480.0,
      "end_time": 204600.0,
      "text": "I would be sent out to a separate trailer"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 204600.0,
      "end_time": 206100.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s why I didn&#39;t really have the"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 206100.0,
      "end_time": 207989.0,
      "text": "English classes and the Math classes"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 207990.0,
      "end_time": 211160.0,
      "text": "because to stick a 12 year old kid in"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 211160.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "with highly, highly mentally handicapped"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216660.0,
      "text": "people for the majority of his education"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 216660.0,
      "end_time": 219320.0,
      "text": "when he&#39;s younger, and he has no... mental"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 219320.0,
      "end_time": 221859.0,
      "text": "issues... uh... affects a kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 221860.0,
      "end_time": 225360.0,
      "text": "They gave us a proficiency exam, which was supposed to"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 225360.0,
      "end_time": 228520.0,
      "text": "tell you what your goals and dreams were going to be in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 228520.0,
      "end_time": 231440.0,
      "text": "Teacher took me in a room and I said \"So how did I do"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 231440.0,
      "end_time": 233780.0,
      "text": "on the test\"? And he said I could be a"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 233790.0,
      "end_time": 236970.0,
      "text": "trash collector, or I could work in the"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 236970.0,
      "end_time": 240380.0,
      "text": "military and those were my two options in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 240380.0,
      "end_time": 242900.0,
      "text": "Uh... In fifth grade, a fifth grade"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 242900.0,
      "end_time": 245160.0,
      "text": "teacher got frustrated with me, and he"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 245160.0,
      "end_time": 247829.0,
      "text": "held me after class. Told me that I would"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 247830.0,
      "end_time": 251220.0,
      "text": "never make it... in... junior high, and that"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 251220.0,
      "end_time": 254480.0,
      "text": "they were going to beat me up, and that, uh..."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 254480.0,
      "end_time": 257120.0,
      "text": "I was going to learn my lesson eventually."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 257120.0,
      "end_time": 259280.0,
      "text": "I think 12 or 13 years old, I started"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 259279.0,
      "end_time": 261820.0,
      "text": "breaking into a liquor cabinet, and I would"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 261820.0,
      "end_time": 264460.0,
      "text": "mark the bottles, and then"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 264460.0,
      "end_time": 267800.0,
      "text": "fill them back with water after I got drunk..."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 267500.0,
      "end_time": 270380.0,
      "text": "...uh, to kill the pain, you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 270380.0,
      "end_time": 273940.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t understand the agony... of..."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 273940.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "I want something, so bad. But it&#39;s just not for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279960.0,
      "text": "Aaron was a totally different story because he has"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 279960.0,
      "end_time": 282680.0,
      "text": "severe dyslexia. He came home one day"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 282680.0,
      "end_time": 286880.0,
      "text": "and... he was really upset. And they- I said why"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 286880.0,
      "end_time": 288600.0,
      "text": "and they said because they gave him a"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 288600.0,
      "end_time": 290250.0,
      "text": "proficiency exam and they told him he"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 290250.0,
      "end_time": 292650.0,
      "text": "could be a trash collector, or he could"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 292650.0,
      "end_time": 293760.0,
      "text": "be in the military."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 293760.0,
      "end_time": 297340.0,
      "text": "He was often times, just passed to the next grade level"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 297340.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "um... because... whelp, its the next teachers problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 302360.0,
      "text": "you know? I&#39;m not going to deal with it right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 302360.0,
      "end_time": 303740.0,
      "text": "Now I realize that the"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 303740.0,
      "end_time": 305620.0,
      "text": "teachers don&#39;t know how to teach against it."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 305620.0,
      "end_time": 307280.0,
      "text": "And so, when we first started, it was"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 307280.0,
      "end_time": 309400.0,
      "text": "everyday for two hours. And most of that"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 309400.0,
      "end_time": 311580.0,
      "text": "time was a lot of dealing with his"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 311580.0,
      "end_time": 315560.0,
      "text": "frustrations of... feeling... uh, inferior"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 315560.0,
      "end_time": 318820.0,
      "text": "in-inside and on the outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 318820.0,
      "end_time": 320880.0,
      "text": "And he said to me..."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 321660.0,
      "end_time": 323920.0,
      "text": "...\"I think I annoy my teachers by asking"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 323920.0,
      "end_time": 326350.0,
      "text": "them so many questions, and so I just"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 326350.0,
      "end_time": 329400.0,
      "text": "spend my whole day, my whole school day"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 329400.0,
      "end_time": 331600.0,
      "text": "trying to disappear.\" He would ask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 331600.0,
      "end_time": 333920.0,
      "text": "\"What was the word?\" and she said she didn&#39;t"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 333920.0,
      "end_time": 335820.0,
      "text": "have time to teach each kid"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 335820.0,
      "end_time": 339200.0,
      "text": "individually. Is the goal here for him to"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 339200.0,
      "end_time": 342400.0,
      "text": "read like you, because that&#39;s never going"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 342400.0,
      "end_time": 345700.0,
      "text": "to happen, or is the goal for him to gain"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 345700.0,
      "end_time": 347900.0,
      "text": "knowledge and learn?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 347900.0,
      "end_time": 350320.0,
      "text": "You know, we decided to pull Aaron out of school"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 350320.0,
      "end_time": 355200.0,
      "text": "because...  because no mom likes to, um..."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 356400.0,
      "end_time": 360960.0,
      "text": "see their kids be hurt, and... or broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 360960.0,
      "end_time": 363520.0,
      "text": "When I first met him, he didn&#39;t care because it too-"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 363520.0,
      "end_time": 364919.0,
      "text": "it hurt too much."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 364920.0,
      "end_time": 367900.0,
      "text": "I was dropping Aaron off at school one time, and he said"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 367900.0,
      "end_time": 370390.0,
      "text": "that the teachers were mad at him, and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 370390.0,
      "end_time": 372789.0,
      "text": "said, \"Why?\" And he said, \"Because when I read"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 372790.0,
      "end_time": 375140.0,
      "text": "I hold my book upside down, and they tell me"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 375140.0,
      "end_time": 378960.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;m goofing off. But Dad, I need"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 378960.0,
      "end_time": 381919.0,
      "text": "to hold my book upside down so I can read.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 381920.0,
      "end_time": 383920.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"I know, son.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 383920.0,
      "end_time": 387260.0,
      "text": "I was worried that if Aaron continued on the path that"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 390820.0,
      "text": "he was on... that he was going to hurt himself."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 390820.0,
      "end_time": 395120.0,
      "text": "Aaron and I have spent many times crying together..."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 397200.0,
      "end_time": 402419.0,
      "text": "and, uh... just letting him know it&#39;s going to be okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 402420.0,
      "end_time": 404260.0,
      "text": "you know? I will never let you go."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 404260.0,
      "end_time": 406960.0,
      "text": "Ever. I&#39;m gonna hold your hand the whole way."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 407280.0,
      "end_time": 410599.0,
      "text": "And then the funny thing is... uh, is that they"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 410600.0,
      "end_time": 412880.0,
      "text": "uh, told us they were going to put together"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 412880.0,
      "end_time": 414780.0,
      "text": "this special program they never lost a"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 414780.0,
      "end_time": 416369.0,
      "text": "kid like Aaron again and then I should"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 416370.0,
      "end_time": 419140.0,
      "text": "give them a chance. And then, I believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 419140.0,
      "end_time": 421320.0,
      "text": "that they discontinued Mrs. Jen&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 421320.0,
      "end_time": 423510.0,
      "text": "program six months later and got rid of"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 423510.0,
      "end_time": 426900.0,
      "text": "her, and ended the entire thing that they"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 426900.0,
      "end_time": 427770.0,
      "text": "were going to set up for Aaron so every"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 427770.0,
      "end_time": 429390.0,
      "text": "kid that&#39;s lost in that school is right"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 429390.0,
      "end_time": 431400.0,
      "text": "back at Ground Zero. So I just don&#39;t"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 431400.0,
      "end_time": 434310.0,
      "text": "think it&#39;s changed. I mean, that was 35"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 434310.0,
      "end_time": 436170.0,
      "text": "years ago that that happened to me, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 436170.0,
      "end_time": 439290.0,
      "text": "Aaron... got pulled out of public school"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 439290.0,
      "end_time": 440730.0,
      "text": "because he couldn&#39;t read on the overhead"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 440730.0,
      "end_time": 443160.0,
      "text": "projector... one year ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 444640.0,
      "end_time": 449800.0,
      "text": "I like to go snowboarding... basketball... baseball."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 449800.0,
      "end_time": 451359.0,
      "text": "Life isn&#39;t just about dyslexia."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 451360.0,
      "end_time": 454200.0,
      "text": "I mean, it doesn&#39;t go away. You just learn to work around it."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 454200.0,
      "end_time": 455900.0,
      "text": "I have Aaron listen to his"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 455900.0,
      "end_time": 457859.0,
      "text": "books on tape, now. Fourth grade year"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 457860.0,
      "end_time": 459940.0,
      "text": "he read, uh, two million words or he listened"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 459940.0,
      "end_time": 462480.0,
      "text": "to two million words. In a year&#39;s time he"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 462480.0,
      "end_time": 465600.0,
      "text": "went from reading kindergarten level, to"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 465600.0,
      "end_time": 468390.0,
      "text": "5th grade. Anybody who reads 2 million"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 468390.0,
      "end_time": 469830.0,
      "text": "words and has a 98-percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 469830.0,
      "end_time": 475580.0,
      "text": "comprehensions in school... tested... is not stupid."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 476240.0,
      "end_time": 478360.0,
      "text": "My favorite book I have ever read"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 478360.0,
      "end_time": 479820.0,
      "text": "is \"American Sniper.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 479820.0,
      "end_time": 481880.0,
      "text": "My goal is to give him the skills so that he can"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 481880.0,
      "end_time": 484400.0,
      "text": "eventually go to higher education, and then on"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 484400.0,
      "end_time": 487500.0,
      "text": "into the workforce. And... I want to be there"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 487500.0,
      "end_time": 489780.0,
      "text": "when he graduates and just say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 489780.0,
      "end_time": 493159.0,
      "text": "\"You did it, kiddo.\""
    }
  ]
}